      ### **ignoreScore** test

    .row
      .col-md-6.success
        p:strong Without ignoreScore
        p Enter a single digit to get 100%:

          +textline({name: 'ch01ignoreScore01', regexp: /\d/, pattern: /\d/})
            .progress-box
            .score-box
            .is-done-box
      .col-md-6.success
        p:strong Same code, with ignoreScore:true
        p Enter a single digit to get 100%:

          +textline({name: 'ch01ignoreScore02', regexp: /\d/, pattern: /\d/, ignoreScore: true})
            .progress-box
            .score-box
            .is-done-box

    p Now we have a composite exercise. Each line needs to contain letters to get 100%.
      | See if you can spot which one is ignored.

    +exercise({name: 'ch01ignoreScore03'})
      .progress-box
      .score-box
      .is-done-box
      +textline({name: 'ch01ignoreScore04', regexp: /[A-Z]/, pattern: /[A-Z]/, regexpFlags: 'i', ignoreScore: false})
